descript.abstract: This dataset represents the state boundaries in the USA (no coastline). Data was derived from the detailed US state boundaries in ESRI Data & maps CDs.
descript.purpose: This dataset is used to create the US Map Templates series.
descript.supplinf: This dataset is in shapefile format, in Geographic coordinate system (lattitude-longitude).

citeinfo.title: Internal state boundaries of the United States
